🫶Merge with realistic, anime models on different weights

deliberate_v2

cosplayMix3

The aims of this model

To create a realistic model which could perform better cosplay with anime character on my aesthetics.

Commercial use

This model doesn't allow any commercial use by selling the model, hosting the model on platform.

You could use this model to generate images and take your own responsibility.

CosplayMix3.0 (abandoned)

Completely new merge with different models.

To use version 3 for photorealistic

Don't recommand to add a lot of quality tags, such as

❌8k, intricate details,ultra-detailed,absurdres,real picture, (photorealistic, hyper-realistic:1.2)
